FT  04 OCT 93 / The Russian Crisis: Leaders' plea for backing
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
'I BELIEVE in our common sense and our strength,' declared President Boris
Yeltsin as he mustered support to put down yesterday's turmoil. 'We have a
